## Installing the HID bootloader to STM32 devices


1. Download the STM32Cube(https://www.st.com/en/ecosystems/stm32cube.html)
2. After Installing Connect Your Board to STM32 Cube through serial adapter
3. Upload the File hid_generic_pc13.bin (stm32_files -> F103 -> Low_and_medium_density(for 64k Flash Memory) -> hid_generic_pc13.bin ) and click OK
4. Make sure to change the Jumper before plugging off the board
